Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How's work? Things going well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.23,0:00:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.77,0:00:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Rosemary also doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She's fine.\NShe's made a lot of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's gotten\Nused to school and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I have to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought a photo of Rosemary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you let me see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.91,0:00:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At this restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.98,0:01:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've completely quit drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.18,0:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My life's back in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. This may be the first time\NI've been living a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized how much I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her decide whether\Nshe wants to see you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Some more coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.44,0:03:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of person do you think\Nthis man is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Richard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think you're here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here for counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you,\NI'm not a fortune-teller!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the result of many years\Nspent interviewing clients, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the first person at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy was the one\Nwho discovered Fahren's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Richard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.91,0:04:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Working hard is fine,\Nbut you need time to relax as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be able to see my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You must be\Nlooking forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,– But...\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you see her, you can't\Nregain what you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Be prepared for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens,\Ndon't touch any alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.01,0:04:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.92,0:05:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going back to work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you deal with
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the event that got you\Nkicked off the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.36,0:05:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He was 17 years old...\Na serial murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was drunk on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You cannot escape from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot rid yourself of it.\NBut what's important is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That I move on...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You're a pretty good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that a perfect score?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! I don't give out\Nperfect scores that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, perfect people are boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl Neumann...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A business major with the University\Nof Munich's Economics Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Fahren, he told that prostitute\Nthat he was Schuwald's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether\Nhe was telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But this boy may somehow be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Richard, I'm finished cleaning,\Nso I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Thank you always\Nfor your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not hard work at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty rare for a man\Nliving by himself to be so neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I was pretty bad before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a new picture\Nof your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll be able to see her soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! That's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter will be delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Any girl would be\Nhappy to see her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So were you able to\Nturn in your paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Karl Neumann...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why don't you tell Schuwald\Nthat you're his son?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you also a swindler?\NOr are you the real thing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you really are Schuwald's son...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should know parents always\Nwant to see their children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. She said that\Nshe doesn't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I also...don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...I see. That's fine.\NDon't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.81,0:09:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Get me a whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.74,0:10:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'm going to where Dad is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're an adult and still\Nwant to meet him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you mustn't expect anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You mustn't hate him\Neven if he's cold to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I don't hate him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take this with you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is something your father\Ngave you when you were born.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"The daffodils of Lares bloom proudly\Nwith no one to admire them."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"The trees of Pieria rustle\Nwith no one to mind them."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh, bloody tracks\Nof a nameless man..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Neumann, you've really become\Na wonderful reader.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed that you've\Nmastered Latin in such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm being taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You have a splendid teacher.\NWho is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan... Johan Liebert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan, huh? He's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not only his Latin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also his knowledge of law\Nand economics.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he has a perfected philosophy\Nfor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a boy who has been perfected\Nto the point of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm...Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What if a boy like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he was your real son?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Schuwald actually smiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that you're worthy enough\Nto be his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at us,\Nyou're clearly better than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt ashamed of my envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you tell him who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.60,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Schuwald that you're his real son.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you that I never intended\Nto do that from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd never believe me\Neven if I did tell him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but he'd think that I was\Nsome hyena who's after his fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The life that my mother led\Nuntil she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The way I've been living until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For him to think of me like that\Nwithout knowing these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you're going to\Ntell him who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to make him\Nsee the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't believe anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.71,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have something\Nhe'd have to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.62,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that will make him\Nbelieve that you're his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't have anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.73,0:15:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Think back.\NYou should have something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that I don't have anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan on telling him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why are you\Nlearning Latin from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you want him\Nto be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you\Nwant him to like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of quitting my job\Nreading to him at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll quit already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:16:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan... Just between\Nyou and me...the thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I do have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have no intention of using that\Nto convince him that I'm his son!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My foster parents are coming\Nto visit me next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind. I'm going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so your determination\Ndoesn't waver...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be best if\NI held on to that proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We're glad you're doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried about whether\Nyou were eating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll get fat if I keep eating out,\Nso I'm being careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get fat on\Nyour mother's meals as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they're so delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.56,0:16:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How's college?\NDid you make any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I can talk about\Nanything to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We can tell that you're doing well\Njust by looking at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful to you that I can\Nstudy here like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what is this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been moving around from\Nfoster home to foster home until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but the both of you\Nreally treated me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because\Nyou're a very wonderful kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Mr. Lindner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop calling me\NMr. Lindner already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wii you accept our offer to adopt\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You said to wait a while\Nafter you got into college,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:18:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We trust you.\NYou trust us as well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your true father and mother\Nmight be alive somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.87,0:18:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what we do,\Nwe may never be the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The both of you...\Nare my real father and mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.99,0:18:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a toast! We'll have\Nan especially expensive wine today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.93,0:18:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, could you\Nbring a wine menu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's a special day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:19:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Neumann? It's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was told that you were\Ngoing to quit your part-time job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.57,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's unfortunate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've worked hard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm impressed at how far\Nyou've come with your Latin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's very unfortunate.\NI'll really miss you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's fine with you, could you read\Nsomething to me one last time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the third part\Nof "From Aeolis to Lemnos"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.60,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, that would be nice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"That mysterious sea even wishes\Nfor the death of the god, Phoebus."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"What pleasures could there be"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"other than to wish for the death of\Nthe sons and daughters of Cerberus?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"'Now, go on"Zeus whispers,\N'go on, go on."'
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dance in the temple\Nof the dark gods."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gods of Juno who dwell in the sea,\Nthe earth, and the heavens..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Steal Campania's forbidden apple\Nfrom the summit of the Parthenon..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.38,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and all come here."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"My heart...my desire..."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,"My heart..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Schuwald...that call just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the most pleasant reading\Nthat I have ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you hidden this\Nall this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.94,0:21:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely the rabbit's foot\Nthat I gave to your mother, Margot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a charm to bring you good luck\Nwhen you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I put you through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all thanks to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.32,0:22:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to be working with me\Nas my secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a young man I can trust.
